---
title: Cajun Salmon and Shrimp with Savoury Rice and Blistered Pepper Salsa
description: This surf 'n' surf feast is inspired by the flavours of Big Easy! Juicy shrimp are spooned over roasted salmon and zesty veggie rice, with a pile of fresh, while a smoky tomato-pepper salsa adds an explosion of texture and taste.
